<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 21:10:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美军秘密X-37B太空飞机准备发射到更高轨道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-militarys-secretive-x-37b-spaceplane-ready-launch-higher-orbit-2023-12-28/</link><description>周四，SpaceX 团队再次准备发射军用 X-37B 机器人太空飞机，执行其第七次任务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-militarys-secretive-x-37b-spaceplane-ready-launch-higher-orbit-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>财新网原央行官员因受贿罪获刑16年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-central-bank-official-jailed-16-years-graft-caixin-2023-12-28/</link><description>随着执政的共产党加强对金融业的控制，一名前中国央行官员因受贿、泄露国家机密和内幕交易被判处 16 年零 6 个月的监禁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-central-bank-official-jailed-16-years-graft-caixin-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯在西方冻结的3000亿美元储备是什么以及在哪里？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-where-are-russias-300-billion-reserves-frozen-west-2023-12-28/</link><description>2022年弗拉基米尔·普京总统出兵乌克兰后，美国及其盟国禁止与俄罗斯央行和财政部进行交易，封锁了西方约3000亿美元的俄罗斯主权资产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-where-are-russias-300-billion-reserves-frozen-west-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>会谈取得突破性进展后，中国军方猛烈抨击美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-lashes-out-us-after-breakthrough-talks-2023-12-28/</link><description>周四，在中美两国高级军事官员恢复高层会谈一周后，中国国防部猛烈抨击美国，批评美国继续干涉亚太地区，并称其保持“冷战”思维。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-military-lashes-out-us-after-breakthrough-talks-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>随着美元和美国国债收益率上升，金价触及三周高位后回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-climbs-over-three-week-high-us-rate-cuts-bets-2023-12-28/</link><description>金价在早些时候触及三周多高位后周四回落，因美元和国债收益率的上涨削弱了美联储明年初降息预期的支撑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:22:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-climbs-over-three-week-high-us-rate-cuts-bets-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划到2025年建造全球一半以上的清洁燃料船舶</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-aims-build-over-half-worlds-clean-fuel-powered-ships-by-2025-2023-12-28/</link><description>工业部周四发布的指导方针中，中国设定了到2025年生产全球一半以上使用清洁燃料的船舶的目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-aims-build-over-half-worlds-clean-fuel-powered-ships-by-2025-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>罗纳尔多的阿尔纳斯尔将在亚洲冠军联赛中与沙特队对决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ronaldos-al-nassr-set-all-saudi-showdown-asian-champions-league-2023-12-28/</link><description>克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多 (Cristiano Ronaldo) 的阿尔纳赛尔 (Al-Nassr) 将在亚洲冠军联赛 16 强中对阵沙特职业联赛球队阿尔法耶哈 (Al-Fayha)，四届冠军阿尔希拉尔 (Al-Hilal) 将于二月份亚洲俱乐部锦标赛回归时对阵伊朗的塞帕汉 (Sepahan)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 09:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ronaldos-al-nassr-set-all-saudi-showdown-asian-champions-league-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示不会对菲律宾一再“挑衅”视而不见</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-wont-turn-blind-eye-philippines-repeated-provocations-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国周四表示，在南海一系列冲突导致紧张局势加剧之际，中国不会对菲律宾一再的“挑衅和骚扰”视而不见。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:45:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-wont-turn-blind-eye-philippines-repeated-provocations-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促国民在骚乱中离开缅北地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-nationals-leave-north-myanmar-region-amid-unrest-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国驻缅甸大使馆周四敦促中国公民尽快离开缅北果敢地区老街地区，理由是安全风险日益增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-nationals-leave-north-myanmar-region-amid-unrest-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>美军加强前沿部署 中国敦促地区保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-regional-alert-us-military-steps-up-forward-deployment-2023-12-28/</link><description>在有报道称美国计划恢复对日本发动原子弹轰炸的太平洋机场后，中国国防部周四敦促亚太地区保持高度戒备，因为美国加强了在该地区的军事部署。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-regional-alert-us-military-steps-up-forward-deployment-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>韩国新任国家安全顾问是资深外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-new-national-security-adviser-is-veteran-diplomat-2023-12-28/</link><description>韩国总统尹锡烈办公室周四表示，韩国新任国家安全顾问将由在美国和朝鲜事务方面拥有丰富经验的经验丰富的外交官张浩镇担任。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:37:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-new-national-security-adviser-is-veteran-diplomat-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责台湾“炒作”军事威胁并派遣战机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-is-hyping-up-military-threat-its-own-gain-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国国防部周四指责台湾政府在两周多后的台湾选举前故意“炒作”中国的军事威胁，以获取选举利益，但却再次派战机进入台湾海峡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-taiwan-is-hyping-up-military-threat-its-own-gain-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>三名香港活动人士因“恐怖主义”炸弹阴谋被判最高六年监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-hong-kong-activists-jailed-up-6-years-terrorism-bomb-plot-2023-12-28/</link><description>三名香港活动人士周四被判处最高六年监禁，他们承认与 2021 年大规模民主抗议活动后计划在法院大楼和其他公共基础设施放置炸弹有关的指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/three-hong-kong-activists-jailed-up-6-years-terrorism-bomb-plot-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国小米推出首款电动汽车，计划成为顶级汽车制造商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-smartphone-maker-xiaomi-unveils-first-electric-vehicle-2023-12-28/</link><description>中国智能手机制造商小米周四揭开了其首款电动汽车的面纱，并立即宣布其目标是成为全球五大汽车制造商之一。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 06:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-smartphone-maker-xiaomi-unveils-first-electric-vehicle-2023-12-28/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国12月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-factory-activity-likely-contracted-third-month-2023-12-28/</link><description>路透周四的一项民意调查显示，由于制成品需求疲软，中国制造业活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，这一数据将鼓励更多政策支持的呼声。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-dec-factory-activity-likely-contracted-third-month-2023-12-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>